casebody.data:
Robert Allen POYSON, petitioner,
v.
Charles L. RYAN, Director, Arizona Department of Corrections. No. 13-9097. Supreme Court of the United States May 19, 2014.

Case below, 743 F.3d 1185.

Motion of petitioner to defer consideration of the petition for writ of certiorari denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.
